== 製作 ==
===規劃<!--Development-->===
[[Netflix|Netflix]]在2019年3月19日計劃要拍攝一個六集的迷你劇，此劇由{{le|史考特·法蘭克|Scott Frank}}和{{le|艾倫·史考特|Allan Scott (Scottish screenwriter)}}創作，他們和William Horberg擔任執行導演<ref name="SeriesOrder">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/03/netflix-orders-the-queens-gambit-limited-series-from-scott-frank-anya-taylor-joy-to-star-1202578402/|title=Netflix Orders 'The Queen's Gambit' Limited Series From Scott Frank; Anya Taylor-Joy To Star|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|first=Denise|last=Petski|date=2019-03-19|accessdate=2019-07-20|archive-date=2019-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330065412/https://deadline.com/2019/03/netflix-orders-the-queens-gambit-limited-series-from-scott-frank-anya-taylor-joy-to-star-1202578402/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。迷你劇在2020年10月23日上映，共有七集，比原先規劃的多了一集<ref name="SeriesPremiere">{{cite web|url=https://www.vulture.com/2020/08/the-queens-gambit-trailer-anya-taylor-joy-netflix-chess.html|title=The Queen's Gambit Trailer: Anya Taylor-Joy Dives Into Chess, Drugs, and More Chess|website=Vulture|first=Jackson|last=McHenry|date=2020-08-27|accessdate=2020-08-27|archive-date=2020-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201006052521/https://www.vulture.com/2020/09/the-queens-gambit-trailer-anya-taylor-joy-netflix-chess.html/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|卡洛斯·拉斐爾·里維拉|Carlos Rafael Rivera}}為此劇配樂<ref>{{cite web|url=https://filmmusicreporter.com/2020/08/27/carlos-rafael-rivera-scoring-netflixs-the-queens-gambit/|title=Carlos Rafael Rivera Scoring Netflix's 'The Queen's Gambit'|website=FilmMusicReporter|date=2020-08-27|accessdate=2020-09-01|archive-date=2020-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201018051102/https://filmmusicreporter.com/2020/08/27/carlos-rafael-rivera-scoring-netflixs-the-queens-gambit/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由曾任[[世界國際象棋錦標賽|世界國際象棋錦標賽]]冠軍的[[加里·基莫维奇·卡斯帕罗夫|加里·基莫维奇·卡斯帕罗夫]]以及國際象棋教練{{le|布魯斯·潘德爾菲尼|Bruce Pandolfini}}擔任顧問<ref>{{cite web |url=https://time.com/5901699/queens-gambit-review-netflix/ |title=Netflix's Marvelous The Queen's Gambit Is the Kind of Prestige Drama TV Doesn't Make Anymore |website=Time |first=Judy |last=Berman |date=2020-10-20 |accessdate=2020-10-27 |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027014912/https://time.com/5901699/queens-gambit-review-netflix/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://new.uschess.org/news/queens-gambit-out-today-netflix|title=The Queen's Gambit - Out Today On Netflix!|website=Chess Life|first=John|last=Hartmann|date=2020-10-23|accessdate=2020-10-30|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030224933/https://new.uschess.org/news/queens-gambit-out-today-netflix|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

