===影評家评价=== 
本劇獲得電視影評家盛赞。於[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]整合的評論中，獲得100%的新鮮度、平均得分8.16/10（53名評論家）<ref>{{Cite web|title=《后翼棄兵》Netflix年度零負評人氣劇|url=https://holiday.presslogic.com/article/207705/|accessdate=2020-11-11|work=HolidaySmart 假期日常|language=zh-hk}}</ref>，評論家共識：「这部电视剧并不总是完美的，但在安雅·泰勒-喬伊充满吸引力的表演、不可思议的时代细节和情商写作之间，《后翼棄兵》是一个绝对的胜利。」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/the_queens_gambit/95809|title=The Queen's Gambit: Miniseries (2020)|website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|access-date=2020-11-07|publisher=[[Fandango_Media|Fandango Media]]|archive-date=2020-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027212034/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/the_queens_gambit/95809|dead-url=no}}</ref>。於[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]整合的評論中，獲得了79分（滿分100；28名評論家），屬于“正面评论为主”。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/tv/the-queens-gambit/season-1|title=The Queen's Gambit: Season 1|website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2020-11-02|archive-date=2020-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201008071201/https://www.metacritic.com/tv/the-queens-gambit/season-1|dead-url=no}}</ref>

