===制作公司被控告===
2021年9月16日，格鲁吉亚国际象棋冠军[[诺娜·加普林达什维利|诺娜·加普林达什维利]]向法庭控告Netflix诽谤罪，指对方在电视剧最后一集声称她从没在专业赛事中与男性下棋的说法有误，要求删除相关内容。加普林达什维利事实上经常和男性棋手比赛，包括顶尖选手<ref>{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2021/09/queens-gambit-lawsuit-netflix-nona-gaprindashvili-1234838186/ |title=Netflix Hit With $5M Suit Over “Sexism” Of ‘Queen’s Gambit’ Line About Soviet Chess Legend |website=Deadline |first=Dominic |last=Patten |date=2021-09-16 |access-date=2021-09-17 |archive-date=2022-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220205040419/https://deadline.com/2021/09/queens-gambit-lawsuit-netflix-nona-gaprindashvili-1234838186/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/09/16/arts/television/queens-gambit-lawsuit.html |title=A Chess Pioneer Sues, Saying She Was Slighted in ‘The Queen’s Gambit’ |website=The New York Times |first=Matt |last=Stevens |date=2021-09-16 |access-date=2021-09-17 |archive-date=2022-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220130142023/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/09/16/arts/television/queens-gambit-lawsuit.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

